data.description: Step inside this beautiful home in the Papillion neighborhood of Glenwood Hills! From the moment you walk up, you’re greeted with charm. From the spacious front porch perfect for lounging, to the vaulted ceilings in the living room that really opens up the space. This home has it all! A unique floorplan gives the feel of privacy without losing the open floorplan everyone loves. Basement includes a spacious living space perfect for a theater room or game room. Plus there’s plenty of storage space in the laundry room as well. The home sits on a corner lot and has a fully fenced and spacious backyard. Neighborhood includes a park and has walking trails that lead to Shadow Lake! Close to Shadow Lake shopping center and easy access to 370 to get you wherever you need quick. Don’t miss your chance to check out this Papillion gem!
